# ğŸš€ How to Run This Pipeline

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Add Jenkinsfile to repository

Commit the file named **`Jenkinsfile`** at root.

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Create Jenkins Pipeline Job

* New Item â†’ Pipeline â†’ SCM â†’ Git repository
* Jenkins will auto-detect Jenkinsfile

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Ensure Tools Are Installed on Jenkins Agent

* Docker
* Trivy
* dependency-check
* sonar-scanner or Maven
* Docker Scout
* ZAP (Docker)

### 4ï¸âƒ£ Run the Pipeline

Click **Build Now**.

